sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant FriendSvc as FriendService
participant FriendDb as Mongo_Friend

Note over User,FriendDb: Chặng 2 - Lỗi nghiệp vụ thường gặp
User->>Gateway: Gửi lời mời cho chính mình
Gateway->>FriendSvc: Validate
FriendSvc-->>User: 400 self-friend

User->>Gateway: Gửi lời mời trùng quan hệ
Gateway->>FriendSvc: Validate duplicate
FriendSvc-->>User: 409 duplicate

User->>Gateway: Accept request không tồn tại
Gateway->>FriendSvc: Check relation
FriendSvc-->>User: 404 not found
